snippet: Brian Harman had two eagles in a six-under-par 65 that gave him a one-stroke lead after three rounds of the PGA Tour’s John Deere Classic.
abstract: Brian Harman takes third-round lead at John Deere Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Brian Harman had two eagles in a six-under-par 65 that gave him a one-stroke lead after three rounds of the PGA Tour’s John Deere Classic.

headline.main: Two Eagles Lift Harman at John Deere Classic
